---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Iaido Division"
  description="Introducing the Seishinkai Iaido Division, an iaido (sword-drawing) class in Sapporo. We practice on Sundays at the Seishinkan Headquarters Dojo and welcome members from junior high school students to seniors."
  lang="en"
  path="/en/dojo/iai/"
>
  <section class="dojo-list">
    <div class="page-container">
      <div class="section__title-area">
        <span class="section-label">IAIDO</span>
        <h1 class="section-title">Seishinkai Iaido Division</h1>
      </div>

      <p class="detail-page__lead">
        [Seishinkai Iaido Division]<br />
        The Seishinkai Iaido Division got its start in 2005 (Heisei 17), led by Maekawa Shihan, Muroki Shihan, and the late Mimura Kayoko Shihan, at the Shiroishi Seishinkan Dojo.<br />
        Today we practice at the Seishinkan Headquarters Dojo. About half of our members are women.<br />
        We are currently welcoming new members.<br />
        Seniors aged 60 and over are especially welcome!!<br />
        Members currently range from <strong>junior high school students to 82 years old</strong>
      </p>

      <h2 class="detail-page__heading">A Lifelong Hobby</h2>
      <p>
        <a href="http://karate15.dokkin.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
          >Sundays from 14:00</a
        ><br />
        ※Autumn/Winter/Spring hours<br />
        During the height of summer heat, sessions may begin in the evening instead
      </p>

      <div class="detail-gallery">
        <figure>
          <img
            src="/assets/images/legacy/images/muro.jpg"
            alt="Taku Muroki, Iaido Division Head"
            width="124"
            height="124"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <figcaption>
            <a href="mailto:muroki-taku@seishinryu.info?subject=Iaido Inquiry"
              >Direct Email</a
            >
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure>
          <img
            src="/assets/images/legacy/dojo/iai/img2.jpg"
            alt="An iaido practice session"
            width="322"
            height="171"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </figure>
      </div>

      <p>
        Opening times may be delayed due to traffic conditions, so please wait if this happens.<br />
        ※For inquiries, please contact our office.<br />
        Trial classes are available for 1,000 yen.<br />
        We also offer one-time private seminars (tuition: 5,000–10,000 yen).
      </p>

      <h2 class="detail-page__heading">
        <a
          href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/〒003-0021+北海道札幌市白石区栄通２丁目１−２７/@43.0409785,141.3938016,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x5f0b2bb4690b9e5f:0x622b301003410409!8m2!3d43.0409785!4d141.3959903"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          >2-1-27 Sakaedori, Shiroishi-ku, Sapporo (along Tohoku-dori) — about
          10 min / 800m on foot from Shiroishi Subway Station — Seishinkan
          Headquarters Dojo</a
        >
      </h2>

      <div class="detail-media">
        <a
          href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLyugCVja4s7Kz8vG3OA4GyMEpSKcsDzQV"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
        >
          <img
            src="/assets/images/legacy/dojo/iai/img6.jpg"
            alt="Seishinkai Iaido Division performance video (YouTube)"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </a>
        <p class="detail-media__caption">Performance Video (YouTube)</p>
      </div>

      <div class="detail-media">
        <img
          src="/assets/images/legacy/dojo/iai/img7.jpg"
          alt="Seishinkai Iaido Division practice session"
          width="626"
          height="218"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>

      <h2 class="detail-page__heading">Seishinkai Iaido Division</h2>
      <p>
        ◆ Founded: July 2005 (Heisei 17)<br />
        ◆ Founder: Nobutaka Maekawa (1st Division Head)<br />
        ◆ Current Head: Taku Muroki (2nd Division Head)
      </p>

      <h2 class="detail-page__heading">Early Members of the Seishinkai Iaido Division</h2>
      <div class="detail-media">
        <a
          href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLyugCVja4s7Kz8vG3OA4GyMEpSKcsDzQV"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
        >
          <img
            src="/assets/images/legacy/dojo/iai/img4.jpg"
            alt="Early members of the Seishinkai Iaido Division"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </a>
      </div>

      <h2 class="detail-page__heading">Iaido Division Head, Taku Muroki</h2>
      <div class="detail-media">
        <a
          href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UClIx3Srenlu1ddf5coow83A"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
        >
          <img
            src="/assets/images/legacy/dojo/iai/img3.jpg"
            alt="Taku Muroki, Iaido Division Head (YouTube channel)"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </a>
      </div>
      <p>
        □Enrollment fee ¥7,000<br />
        □Annual fee ¥5,800<br />
        □Base monthly fee ¥6,000/month<br />
        ※¥3,000/month for current Karate Division members
      </p>
      <p class="detail-page__note">
        Please ask us about this when you come for a trial class<br />
        ※Fees are reduced in stages as you advance in rank<br />
        ※You will also need a hakama, iai gi, iai belt, iaito (sword), bokuto
        (wooden sword), soft sword, and other equipment.
      </p>

      <p class="detail-page__back">
        <a href="/en/dojo/">← Back to the Dojo & Class List</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
